  "title": "Production Supervisor (Metal)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Lead and supervise work closely with other sub-contractors within the Fabrication area to meet project schedule</li>\n  <li>Lead and motivate term of workforce including control and supervision of given tasks</li>\n  <li>Ensure procedures, standards and guidelines are followed, maintained and implement corrective/preventive actions</li>\n  <li>Ensure sub-contractors execute their works accurately in accordance to the approved shop-drawings, technical submissions and checklists</li>\n  <li>Resolve technical issue with suppliers and subcontractors</li>\n  <li>Implement works safety, environmental requirements / procedure</li>\n  <li>Implementation of Cost and Quality on site, and to ensure minimum wastage and reworks</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparation of Production Schedule and Production Lists</li>\n</ul>",
